ted to the dynamics in the inner\ndisk as well, as both its frequency and R_in vary significantly on the\nhorizontal branch but become relatively constant on the normal branch.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Jul 2012 20:01:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
