p is also introduced\ncalled the \"Harmonic sawtooth\" whose Mellin transform is the (appropritately\nscaled) Riemann zeta function. These maps are within the family of what might\nbe called \"deterministic chaos\". Some number theoretic definitions are also\nrecalled.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Jul 2012 21:05:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-06"}
