e wide-field near-IR surveys such as the\nVISTA and EUCLID surveys. [Abridged]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Jul 2012 08:38:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Nov 2012 10:28:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-04"}
